---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1152px] mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-[1.953rem] font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] text-center mb-12 tracking-tight">
      The problem with AI-assisted development
    </h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--border-default)] bg-[var(--bg-surface)] p-6 lg:p-8">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-error/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-error" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">AI tools lack project context</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Your AI coding tools don't know your product vision, design system, tech stack decisions, or team standards. Every prompt starts from zero, producing inconsistent code that doesn't match your project.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--border-default)] bg-[var(--bg-surface)] p-6 lg:p-8">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-warning/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-warning" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 12c0-1.232-.046-2.453-.138-3.662a4.006 4.006 0 0 0-3.7-3.7 48.678 48.678 0 0 0-7.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 0 0-3.7 3.7c-.017.22-.032.441-.046.662M19.5 12l3-3m-3 3-3-3m-12 3c0 1.232.046 2.453.138 3.662a4.006 4.006 0 0 0 3.7 3.7 48.656 48.656 0 0 0 7.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 0 0 3.7-3.7c.017-.22.032-.441.046-.662M4.5 12l3 3m-3-3-3 3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Specs drift from reality</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Documentation written at kickoff becomes stale within weeks. Your AI tools reference outdated specs, or worse, get no context at all — leading to decisions that contradict your evolving codebase.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
